---
title: Mango Chutney Tofu Curry with Crispy Chana Dal
description: This tofu curry cooked with sweet mango chutney, fragrant spices and curry paste is a taste extravaganza! You'll spoon this mouthwatering curry over buttery, cilantro-flecked rice, then garnish it with crispy chana dal to create a dish that will have everyone around the dinner table drooling!
